dct_title_s: Welcome to the Presidio of San Francisco
dct_description_sm: compiled by Bernard Bennett and drawn by Edwin Wong ; Presidio of San Francisco, California, Master Planning Office, Directorate of Facilities Engineer, Headquarters Presidio of San Francisco.
"Since 1776 three flags have flown over the Presidio. Spain 1776-1822 -- Mexico: 1822-1846 -- United States: 1846 - to the present."
